reviewText: This video is just terrible.  The action is awful and the actors/actresses are obscure.  I understand that this is a retro product, but it's not even good for nostalgia's sake.  Skip it.

I bought this just for lisa ann. But was greatly disappointed when I put it on n saw that there was no action scenes. Its just here stripping. Thats it. Maybe I would of like it more if I was 15. But just wasn't enough to enjoy. N only reason I even gave it 2stars is just for how hot lisa ann is. Other then that it wasn't what I hoped for.
The Retro Sex Symbols of the 90's 2 is still in style. Lisa Ann is beautiful and has a very good body. Lovette has an equally good body but it's Lisa that shine in this DVD.
The show/shows was/were repetitious and boring; no more exciting than an animated version of a Playboy magazine centerfold., in my opinion
